            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <h3>How should I store raw pet food?</h3>
                    <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p><strong>Freezer storage:</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Keep frozen at -18¬∞C or below</li>
                        <li>Use within 6-12 months (varies by protein)</li>
                        <li>Portion into meal-sized containers before freezing</li>
                        <li>Label with contents and date</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><strong>Refrigerator storage:</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Thaw in refrigerator, never at room temperature</li>
                        <li>Use thawed food within 24-48 hours</li>
                        <li>Store in sealed containers on bottom shelf</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
