                    <h3>Can I refreeze thawed raw food?</h3>
                    <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>It's not recommended to refreeze completely thawed raw food due to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Potential bacterial growth during thaw time</li>
                        <li>Loss of texture and nutritional quality</li>
                        <li>Increased risk of spoilage</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>Instead: portion meals before initial freezing, or use thawed food within the safe timeframe.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

